title: SET_WEATHER_CYCLE_ENTRY
content:
0xD264D4E1// SetWeatherCycleEntry
BOOL SET_WEATHER_CYCLE_ENTRY(int index, char* typeName, int timeMult);Parameters:index: The index of the entry to set. Must be between 0 and 255typeName: The name of the weather type for this cycletimeMult: The relative duration of this cycle, which is multiplied by msPerCycle during 'APPLY_WEATHER_CYCLES'. Must be between 1 and 255Returns: Returns true if all parameters were valid, otherwise false.
